    Well here you are, the final encounter.  This is a standby
for quests.  Quite often, even if the quest is not combat oriented,
you will be required to overcome some enemy bigger, tougher, and
meaner than yourself in order to get what you need to complete
the quest.  This one is no different.  However, because you will
be in at least one guild, more than likely, to do your questing,
you will usually have some guild powers at your disposal to
assist you in this matter.  Well since you aren't and you don't,
respectively, I'm going to help you out.  This primer
that you're holding is capable of helping you defeat the goblin
chieftain and the nasty witch doctor.  I'm not going to tell you
exactly what it does, but the syntax to bring it about is
'newbieblast.'  So when you're ready to take them on, go for it.
